What role does the help desk professional play within an organization, particularly in relation to customers?
Customers and users depend on the IT staff to keep systems available and operationa.The help desk professional is often the “face” of the IT staff that customers see and, right or wrong, customers often make judgments about the entire organization based on their interactions with a help desk professional.

