How do writing skills and critical thinking skills play a vital role in the work of help desk technicians?
Writing skills are very important . for example lets say one pc would constintly have a blue screen and it took you 2 hours to solve the issue . If you have good writing skills and break down the issue and how you solved someone can open you document up when the problem accours again and be able to fix it in fraction of the time.
